 hng phi  li thng tin nu cha c s ng .</p>\r\n<p>5. Phng tin v cng c  ngi dng tip cn v chnh<br />Khch hng hon ton c th yu cu 4men.com.vn cung cp hoc xa b thng tin ca chnh mnh nu c nhu cu, 4MEN(R) hon ton khng s dng hoc chnh sa thng tin khch hng.</p>\r\n<p>6. Cam kt bo mt thng tin c nhn khch hng<br />- Thng tin ca bn, d cng hay t, s khng c bn, trao i, chuyn nhng, hoc cho bt k cng ty khc cho bt k l do no, m khng cn s ng  ca bn<br />- Tt c cc thng tin nhy cm ch c th truy cp bi nhng ngi c y quyn c quyn truy cp v c yu cu  gi cho cc thng tin b mt.</p>','',1,11,'2018-11-14 09:27:36',640,'','2018-11-14 09:27:39',640,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2018-11-14 09:27:36','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}','{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}',2,0,'','',1,0,'{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}',0,'*','',''),(12,83,'Chnh sch cookie','chinh-sach-cookie','<div><strong>Chnh sch cookie ca ti website 4men.com.vn ca thng hiu thi trang 4MEN(R)</strong><br /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>4MEN s dng cookie trnh duytcho nhiu mc ch trn cc trang web v trong thng tin lin lc email ca chng ti cung cp dch v v nng cao tri nghim ngi dng, ngi truy cp website, khch hng,... Chng ti hin ang trin khai cch thc chia s nhng ti nguyn cho cc i tc tin cy v nng cao tri nghim trn trang web ca h. Chnh sch ny m t cc loi cookie m chng ti s dng (v c i tc ca chng ti s dng), chng c dng lm g v bn c th thay i cc ty chn cookie yca mnh nh th no.<br /><br /><strong>Cookie l g?</strong><br /><br />Cookie l cc bite, dngthng tin nh c trnh duyt ca bn lu tr trn  cng my tnh ca bn. Mi lnbn truy cp li trang web trn h thng ca4MEN(R), trnh duyt web ca bn gi nhng cookie ny tr li cho chng ti  chng ti c th ty chnh tri nghim ca bn  ph hp hn vi s thch v ty chn ca bn hoc ch n gin l h tr bn ng nhp  s dng cc dch v ca chng ti.<br /><br /><strong>4MEN(R) s dng cookie no?</strong><br /><br />Nhngcookie m chng ti s dng cho php chng ti nhn ra mi ngi dng quay li v thng tin lin quan ca h  bn khng cn nhp nhiu ln cng mt thng tin. Chng cng gip chng ti hiu c cc dnglu lng truy cp ca khch truy cp qua trang web ca chng ti,  chng ti c th nng cao kh nng s dng.<br /><br /><strong>Hy xem mt s loi cookie c s dng trn trang web ca chng ti:</strong><br /><br /><strong>Cookie thit yu</strong><br />4MEN(R) c th s dng cc cookie thit yu  cho php bn nhn c cc dch v bn yu cu qua websiteca chng ti. Nu khng c nhng cookie ny, cc dch v bn  yu cu s khng th c cung cp.<br /></div>\r\n<div><strong>Chng hn, nhng cookie ny c th c s dng :</strong></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Vn hnh v ghi nh cc mt hng bn chn/t vo gi hng khi s dng</li>\r\n<li>Cho php bn truy cp vo cc khu vc an ton trn trang web ca chng ti m khng cn lin tc ng nhp vo dch v</li>\r\n<li>Ghi nh hnh ng trc y m bn  thc hin (nh hon thnh biu mu trc tuyn) khi iu hng tr li trang trong cng mt phin</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div><br /><strong>Cc m-un cookie hot ng</strong><br />4MEN(R)c th s dng cc cookie hot ng  thu thp thng tin v cctrang web, qung co (Uy tn: google, facebook) v thng tin lin lc email ca chng ti c s dng v  cnh bo chng ti nu c li xy ra. Nhng cookie ny c th c s dng  thu thp cc d thiuthng tin kh chi tit khi bn tri nghim \"lt web\" trn websitenh: Trang truy cp ln cui, s trang  truy cp, th lin lc qua email c c m khng, phn no trn trang web hoc th lin lc qua email ca chng ti c nhn vo v thi gian gia cc ln nhn. Mc d thng tin ny c th c kt hp vi cc chi tit nh a ch IP, min hoc thng tin trnh duyt ca bn, thng tin ch c phn tch tng hp vi thng tin t ngi dng khc v khng c thc hin theo cch thc c th nhn dng bn trc tip.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><strong>Chng hn, nhng cookie ny c th c s dng trn trang web ca chng ti :</strong></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Phn tch v ci thin hot ng v thit k ca cc trang web, qung co v th lin lc qua email ca chng ti</li>\r\n<li>Tnh s lng phn hi vi qung co ca chng ti  ci thin hiu qu ca qung co</li>\r\n<li>o s lng li hin th trn trang web ca chng ti  ci thin cc khiu ni v dch v v qun l ca chng ti</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div><br /><strong>Cookie gii thiu</strong><br />4MEN(R) c th truy cp cc cookie gii thiu c cc trang web ca i tc kinh doanh ca chng ti gi ti thit b ca bn. Nhng cookie ny c s dng mi khi i tc kinh doanh ca chng ti gii thiu ai  ti trang web ca chng ti d lt truy cp ca ngi  c dn n vic mua sn phm hoc dch v ca 4MEN(R) hay khng. Thng tin ny c th c tit l cho i tc kinh doanh ca chng ti, nhng ch theo cch n danh v khng theo cch c th nhn dng bn trc tip.<br />Chng ti s dng thng tin ny  p ng cc ngha v theo hp ng ca chng ti vi cc i tc kinh doanh v  h tr h ci thin hiu qu trang web ca h.<br /><br /><strong>Cookie chc nng</strong><br />4MEN(R)c th s dng cookie chc nng, tuy khng thit yu nhng cho php nhiu tnh nng hu ch khc nhau trn trang web ca chng ti.<br />Chng hn, nhng cookie ny c th c s dng trn trang web ca chng ti :</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Ghi nh cc ty chn m bn  chn trong ln truy cp trc vo trang web ca chng ti, nh quc gia/ngn ng, s thch ca bn v cch trnh by trang web ca chng ti (chng hn, b cc, c ch, mu sc, v.v..),  bn khng cn phi thng bo li cho chng ti</li>\r\n<li>Ghi nh cu tr li cho cc cu hi m trang web ca chng ti  hi bn, nh khng mun tham gia bng cu hi v s hi lng ca khch hng,  chng ti khng hi li bn na</li>\r\n<li>Pht hin liu dch v  c cung cp cho bn cha, chng hn, cung cp dch v tr gip trc tuyn vi ngi h tr</li>\r\n<li>Cung cp thng tin cho php mt dch v ty chn hot ng, nh xem video trc tuyn hoc bnh lun trong blog</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div><br /><strong>Cookie nhm mc tiu hoc gii thiu sn phm</strong><br />Cookie nhm mc tiu hoc gii thiu sn phmc th c s dng trn trang web ca chng ti  phn pht sn phmc lin quan hn n bn v s thch ca bn. Nhng cookie ny c th thu thp thng tin kh chi tit v thi quen duyt web ca bn trn trang website ca 4MEN(R)(nh bn  nhn vo sn phm v dch v no). Chng c th c s dng  nhn dng khi bn truy cp li trang web ca chng ti v/hoc truy cp trang web l mt phn trong mng li i tc qung co ca chng ti.<br />Chng hn, nhng cookie ny c th c s dng  thu thp thng tin v cc sn phm v dch v ca 4MEN(R) m bn  duyt hoc  thm vo gi hng ca mnh trn trang web ca chng ti :</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Cc i tc qung co ca chng ti (google, facebook, cc doanh nghip qung co trc tuyt trong nc,..)c th cung cp cho bn qung co trn cc trang web khc ca htrong mng li qung co ca h v cc sn phm v dch v ca 4MEN(R) m bn  xem</li>\r\n<li>Chng ti c th gii hn s ln bn nhn thy qung co cng nh o hiu qu ca mt chin dch qung co</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div><br />Nhng cookie ny c th c 4MEN(R) v/hoc i tc qung co ca chng ti lu tr v truy cp.<br /><br /><strong>Cookie bn th ba</strong><br />Vic bn s dng trang web ca chng ti c th dn n mt s cookie c lu tr m khng c 4MEN(R) kim sot. iu ny c th xy ra khi Trang bn ang truy cp bao gm cc ni dung c hin th t trang web bn th ba v s dn n vic bn nhn cookie t cc dch v bn th ba ny. Tuy nhin, s khng c thng tin c nhn no c lu tr trong nhng cookie ny, tr khi bn ng nhp vo ti khon ca mnh.<br />Chng hn, nhng cookie ny c th n t:</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>YouTube hoc Facebook</li>\r\n<li>Cc nh khai thc mng ng tin cy</li>\r\n<li>Cc c quan truyn thng c tr ph</li>\r\n<li>Cc chng trnh tip th ca chnh 4MEN(R)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><br />4MEN(R) khng kim sot vic lu tr hoc truy cp vo nhng cookie ny. Bn nn xem xt chnh sch bo mt v cookie ca cc dch v ny  tm hiu v cch s dng cookie ca nhng bn th ba ny.<br /><br /><strong>Mua hng vi 4MEN(R)</strong><br />Chng ticam kt bo v quyn ring t ca khch hng v chng ti  thc hin cc bin php mnh nhm m bo rng thng tin chng ti thu thp t bn s c an ton v b mt. Cookie ca 4MEN(R) khng c s dng  truy cp vo thng tin  nhp trn my ch an ton. Bn ch c th truy cp thng tin ny khi nhp tn v s tham chiu n t hng ca mnh.<br /><br /><strong>Cch iu chnh ci t cookie ca bn</strong><br />Hu ht cc trnh duyt s cho php bn xa cookie khi  cng my tnh ca mnh, chn chp nhn cookie hoc nhn cnh bo trc khi cookie c lu tr.<br /><br /><strong>iu g xy ra nu cookie b v hiu ha?</strong><br />Nu bn chn hoc xa cookie, chng ti c th khng khi phc c bt k ty chn hoc ci t ty chnh no bn  ch nh trc  v kh nng c nhn ha tri nghim trc tuyn ca bn s b hn ch.<br /><br />Tm hiu cch thay i ci t ca bn cho:</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Google Chrome</strong>:http://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647?hl=en</li>\r\n<li><strong>Mozilla Firefox</strong>:http://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/enable-and-disable-cookies-website-preferences</li>\r\n<li><strong>Internet Explorer</strong>:http://support.microsoft.com/kb/196955</li>\r\n<li><strong>Safari</strong>:http://support.apple.com/kb/PH5042</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','',1,2,'2018-11-14 09:27:58',640,'','2018-11-14 09:27:58',0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2018-11-14 09:27:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"target